{
  "name": "RPlog_We_Are_All_All_of_Us_Dust",
  "title": "The Bomber in the Yarith Lobby",
  "summary": "During a hastily relocated medical conference at the Yarith Hotel on Cloud City, a quiet, confused man in a long coat seals the lobby doors and reveals he is wearing a wired explosive vest, repeating the phrase \"we are all, all of us, dust.\" Crestian Tarasar, Doctor Lynae, the Zeltron administrator Quinne, the technician Selko, the spacer Vance, and the doctor Druze are caught in the lobby as panic spreads. Quinne tries to talk the bomber down with soothing pheromones while Selko stuns him; the man's detonator fails, but he dies in a seizure and the device begins beeping toward a delayed explosion. Vance restrains the corpse and Selko blasts open a window, through which Druze and Vance hurl the body just before it detonates harmlessly outside, painting the hotel's exterior. With the crisis averted and Lynae unfusing the doors for emergency crews, the shaken survivors retire to the bar, puzzling over the bomber's identity and motive.",
